    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "九个节点，顺序是Redis-Etcd-Redis-Redis-负载均衡-工作节点-Redis-Etcd-负载均衡-回到Redis。这个序列对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。每个节点都是单向箭头连接，形成循环。",
